{"id":1841,"date":"2023-04-27T07:04:24","date_gmt":"2023-04-27T07:04:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/?page_id=1841"},"modified":"2023-04-27T15:43:56","modified_gmt":"2023-04-27T15:43:56","slug":"single-service","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/single-service\/","title":{"rendered":"Single Service"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"1841\" class=\"elementor elementor-1841\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-696175b elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"696175b\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-e137c03\" data-id=\"e137c03\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fcfb4f5 aleft elementor-widget elementor-widget-wgl-double-heading\" data-id=\"fcfb4f5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"wgl-double-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wgl-double-heading\"><h3 class=\"dblh__title-wrapper\"><span class=\"dblh__title dblh__title-1\">Beard Trim<\/span><\/h3><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d236b0e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d236b0e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><em>Beard trimming is an essential part of maintaining a well-groomed and stylish beard. Regular trimming helps to keep your beard neat, tidy, and free from split ends, which can make it look unruly and unkempt. When it comes to beard trimming, there are a few key things to keep in mind.<\/em><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2283cc0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"2283cc0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-369ecf7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"369ecf7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"870\" height=\"460\" src=\"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/service-s-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1845\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/service-s-1.jpg 870w, https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/service-s-1-300x159.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/service-s-1-768x406.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 870px) 100vw, 870px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9bd9b2b elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"9bd9b2b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-205585f aleft elementor-widget elementor-widget-wgl-double-heading\" data-id=\"205585f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"wgl-double-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wgl-double-heading\"><h3 class=\"dblh__title-wrapper\"><span class=\"dblh__title dblh__title-1\">common types of beard trims<\/span><\/h3><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4251694 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4251694\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Before trimming your beard, it&#8217;s also important to decide on the length and style you want to achieve. This will help you to determine how much hair to remove and where to trim. It&#8217;s also a good idea to start with a longer length and gradually work your way down, as it&#8217;s easier to take more off than to add it back.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-90bf87d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"90bf87d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"bladehub_dot list_primary_color\"><li><span style=\"font-weight: 500; color: var(--bladehub-header-font-color);\">Classic Beard:<\/span> This is a full beard that is allowed to grow naturally. It is typically trimmed along the neck and cheeks to maintain a neat and clean appearance.<\/li><li><span style=\"font-weight: 500; color: var(--bladehub-header-font-color);\">Stubble Beard:<\/span> Stubble is a short beard that is maintained at a length of 1-2mm. It can be achieved by using a trimmer on the lowest setting or by letting a full beard grow for a few days before trimming it down.<\/li><li><span style=\"font-weight: 500; color: var(--bladehub-header-font-color);\">Short Beard:<\/span> A short beard is typically trimmed to a length of 2-4cm. It can be styled in a variety of ways, including a goatee or a soul patch.<\/li><li><span style=\"font-weight: 500; color: var(--bladehub-header-font-color);\">Long Beard:<\/span> A long beard is typically trimmed to a length of 7cm or longer. It can be styled in a variety of ways, including a ducktail or a full beard with a styled mustache.<\/li><li><span style=\"font-weight: 500; color: var(--bladehub-header-font-color);\">Mustache Trim:<\/span> This involves trimming and shaping the mustache to create a specific style, such as a handlebar or a horseshoe.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a514229 aleft elementor-widget elementor-widget-wgl-double-heading\" data-id=\"a514229\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"wgl-double-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wgl-double-heading\"><h3 class=\"dblh__title-wrapper\"><span class=\"dblh__title dblh__title-1\">our skilled barbers<\/span><\/h3><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-413fe93 aleft elementor-widget elementor-widget-wgl-team\" data-id=\"413fe93\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"wgl-team.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<section class=\"wgl_module_team\"><div class=\"team__members grid-col--2\"><article class=\"team__member\"><div class=\"member__wrapper\"><div class=\"member__media\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/team\/paul-newman\/\" class=\"member__thumbnail\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/team-s-5-830x820.jpg\" class=\"thumbnail__featured\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/div><div class=\"member__info-wrapper\"><div class=\"member__info\"><div class=\"member__meta-wrapper\"><div class=\"member__highlighted\">BARBER<\/div><\/div><h2 class=\"member__name\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/team\/paul-newman\/